{"tid":130002,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"富田真由被當街追斬34刀案件續審 目擊證人形容「好像看到在捕獵野生動物」","createTime":"2017-02-22T05:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T05:22:28.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb94af172df473d913bc4cee7b4ae019ef387bd","tid":130002,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"21歲日本女偶像富田真由遭砍事件於20日開庭，21日進入第2日公審。除了目擊者以證人身分到場，她的母親更當庭淚崩指控被告：「這是殺人！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2349/d2349562.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2349%2Fd2349562.jpg&h=44ee16d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《報知體育》報導，富田真由母親回憶當時得知愛女發生意外，電話中一度被醫生告知「可能已經來不及了」，趕到醫院時，見到女兒正在動手術，「她滿臉是血，整張臉都浮腫起來，我不禁自問這真的是我的女兒嗎？」邊哭邊說當時不斷重複對女兒喊話「加油！加油！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2349/d2349560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2349%2Fd2349560.jpg&h=06cb11a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲富田真由遭砍當時大量出血，臉部浮腫認不出來。<br />\n<br />\n有關女兒的復原情況，富田媽媽表示現在手指、嘴巴都呈現麻痺狀態，每周都去醫院復健，「她每天都按摩嘴巴、舌頭體操，她說過感覺治不好了，但是真的拼命地在復健，我這當媽媽的看了都好難受。」此外，她也指出被告岩埼友宏的家人，在案件後沒有任何聯繫，公審也沒到場，更憤怒地說：「我女兒的命是救回來了，但是遇上這狀況很可能會死，我認為這是一起殺人事件。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2349/d2349558.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2349%2Fd2349558.jpg&h=eca336d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲富田真由媽媽淚控這是殺人事件。<br />\n<br />\n除了媽媽的證詞，一名女性目擊者也出庭作證。而她當時距離案發現場僅有數公尺，形容「好像看到在捕獵野生動物」，並透露聽到受害者叫喊「為什麼？為什麼？」據悉，富田真由遭砍34刀，岩埼友宏的辯護律師則提出支付日幣200萬元（約台幣55萬元）的賠償金。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2349/d2349559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2349%2Fd2349559.jpg&h=20093646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲目擊者形容當時像看到野生動物被捕獵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lCW3V_AjLiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlCW3V_AjLiA&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=601f7aba\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lCW3V_AjLiA</a>"},{"pid":"3a0e4fd650c53c6ed8137985dbf9cd0613b59284","tid":130002,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99817e47009e7084d9b706a01f1897bed04ea1bf","tid":130002,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:47:29.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b6a0335e3dc799425c3048ba2f292f65d262d9","tid":130002,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:55:46.000Z","msg":"賠咁撚少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a064b4805165d12b0d0e0ea29b6e0a4151578ae","tid":130002,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"死刑"},{"pid":"96c002c18b0c97d4d7feab2fc23eea8d296837c8","tid":130002,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"個犯同波多野合作過架屌"},{"pid":"04e5a4e14babc016d3c1555c3093608766eb7ea5","tid":130002,"uid":57409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個犯同波多野合作過架屌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}